WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.500
My fiancee is...

2
00:00:06.880 --> 00:00:07.980
Early snow

3
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:12.200
The first snow.

4
00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.540
Every day I get to know you, I am very happy.

5
00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:19.540
Are you?

6
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:21.980
Start a family with me.

7
00:00:24.040 --> 00:00:24.840
What?

8
00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:28.500
I agree.

9
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.460
Remember what?

10
00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:40.500
Can't you see?

11
00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:42.140
Remember who wants to get married.

12
00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:44.140
I remember.

13
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:45.860
You're kidding, right?

14
00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:47.300
I'm not kidding.

15
00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:51.580
The woman I want to marry in my life can only be without a future.

16
00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:57.660
I can't believe you promised me you'd marry me in four years.

17
00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.980
Have you forgotten that I saved you?

18
00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:02.180
This road is more deceitful than you.

19
00:01:03.400 --> 00:01:05.200
Saving me 20 years ago was bleeding.

20
00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:06.700
It's not you.

21
00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:07.680
Blood.

22
00:01:07.680 --> 00:01:08.900
Tell you your love for me

23
00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:10.900
His umbrella. I saved you.

24
00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.460
We're still talking.

